that make eyes open wide!

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0002

land of many famous artist!

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0003

made by Gulan master carver!

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0004

Hanahana should ask Mamapon to
buy one, so can display proud in room!

rows.label: tlk42200121_03_msg0005

as master of trading.
